The work of the Kingdom,
in my lifetime and before,


48:50.010 --> 48:58.718
Provides me with your written Word, 
the truth, and so much more.


48:58.718 --> 49:06.893
Your faithful slave, discreet and wise, 
provides increasing light


49:06.893 --> 49:17.336
And sends out men who shepherd me 
with loving oversight.


49:17.337 --> 49:25.145
I know expectations 
at conventions will be met.


49:25.145 --> 49:33.487
And afterward, I always say,
