You give us the honor 
to be workers on your side,


50:50.130 --> 50:58.472
Our ministry that lets us show 
the love we feel inside.


50:58.472 --> 51:06.647
The depth of understanding 
and the peace of mind you give,


51:06.647 --> 51:16.824
They teach us what is pure and true; 
they show the way to live.


51:16.823 --> 51:25.365
The songs that express 
what’s in my heart so very well


51:25.365 --> 51:33.440
And Fam’ly Worship ev’nings 
give your spirit room to dwell.


51:33.440 --> 51:42.315
Our unity, despite whatever language 
we might speak,


51:42.315 --> 51:51.000
Proves that our loving brotherhood 
in this world is unique.


51:52.392 --> 52:08.842
We marvel at your work
And what the Kingdom’s done so far.


52:08.842 --> 52:16.000
We cherish Kingdom rule.


52:17.217 --> 52:25.325
We grow in faith 
to realize the kind of God you are.


52:25.325 --> 52:37.000
We look ahead to blessings 
that your Kingdom soon will bring.


52:46.780 --> 52:48.615
That’s beautiful. 


52:48.615 --> 52:50.817
And how can we show our appreciation 


52:50.817 --> 52:54.120
for Jehovah’s provisions in a practical way? 


52:54.120 --> 52:58.258
By taking seriously 
our God-given assignment to preach. 


52:58.258 --> 53:00.260
And we have seen developments 


53:00.260 --> 53:02.828
in our preaching methods 
in the past few years.


53:02.828 --> 53:07.433
For example, in 2001, 
with the Governing Body’s approval, 


53:07.433 --> 53:10.836
our brothers in France 
started using a variety of methods


53:10.837 --> 53:15.175
to carry out our public witnessing, 
including the use of carts. 


53:15.175 --> 53:18.612
The trial resulted 
in many good experiences. 


53:18.612 --> 53:21.815
As a result, in 2011, 


53:21.815 --> 53:24.250
a pilot project with cart witnessing 


53:24.250 --> 53:28.722
in New York City, U.S.A., was approved.


53:28.722 --> 53:31.190
Since Manhattan, in New York City, 


53:31.190 --> 53:35.362
had a ratio of 1 Jehovah’s Witness
to 657 inhabitants, 


53:35.362 --> 53:37.497
this was a perfect choice. 


53:37.497 --> 53:41.000
That was the beginning 
of a pilot program in Manhattan. 


53:42.868 --> 53:46.071
The program lasted one year, 
using many graduates 


53:46.072 --> 53:49.509
from what was then 
the Bible School for Christian Couples.


53:49.508 --> 53:51.878
Although different tables 
were used at the time, 


53:51.878 --> 53:53.880
it was evident that a mobile cart 


53:53.880 --> 53:55.982
had many advantages. 


53:55.982 --> 53:58.819
As a result, today, 
Jehovah’s Witnesses are well-known 


53:58.818 --> 54:01.721
for their public witnessing using carts  


54:01.722 --> 54:03.490
designed to display their literature. 


54:03.490 --> 54:04.890
By means of this method, 


54:04.890 --> 54:08.127
good news from the Bible 
can be taken to many places 


54:08.127 --> 54:12.000
and easily becomes available 
to countless people.


54:13.433 --> 54:16.670
These carts include different posters that: 


54:16.670 --> 54:19.672
call attention 
to our well-known publications, 


54:19.672 --> 54:23.310
invite people to accept 
free home Bible studies, 


54:23.310 --> 54:27.347
and direct passersby to our official website. 


54:27.347 --> 54:32.000
Here are just a few examples of how 
this method has had many good results.


