55:49.062 --> 55:51.397
I work as a driver and spent most of my life 


55:51.397 --> 55:53.534
traveling all over Peru. 


55:53.533 --> 55:57.936
Because of this, I had problems 
with the woman I was living with. 


55:57.937 --> 56:01.000
I never spent time at home 
and practically lived in the truck.


56:05.945 --> 56:08.347
I would see Jehovah’s Witnesses preaching 


56:08.347 --> 56:10.384
on the streets near the buses. 


56:10.383 --> 56:12.785
But since I was always driving, 


56:12.785 --> 56:15.000
I couldn’t park or even talk to them. 


56:16.522 --> 56:20.260
But once, I saw some Witnesses 
preaching in a public square. 


56:20.260 --> 56:22.328
So I went up to them to ask them 


56:22.328 --> 56:25.000
what the Bible says about family matters.


56:27.400 --> 56:30.000
This marked a change in my life. 


56:32.072 --> 56:35.000
My girlfriend and I 
began attending meetings, 


56:36.743 --> 56:40.780
and then we got married and got baptized. 


56:40.780 --> 56:43.000
Now we are Jehovah’s Witnesses.


56:45.585 --> 56:50.257
As Annies and I were standing by our cart, 
we met young Sudharshan. 


56:50.257 --> 56:54.260
Annies showed him our tract 
Can the Dead Really Live Again? 


56:54.260 --> 56:57.063
He was surprised and said, 
“How is it possible?” 


56:57.063 --> 56:59.998
When she explained to him Acts 24:15, 


56:59.998 --> 57:04.503
he exclaimed: “I am a Christian. 
I never knew this!” 


57:04.503 --> 57:06.873
I asked him, 
“Would you like to learn more 


57:06.873 --> 57:09.175
about such wonderful things 
from the Bible?” 


57:09.175 --> 57:12.578
He asked, 
“Can you tell me right now?” 


57:12.578 --> 57:15.915
There and then, I discussed the first chapter 
of the Bible Teach book. 


57:15.915 --> 57:18.083
That’s how it started.


57:18.083 --> 57:20.520
Sudharshan brought his friend, Sagar. 


57:20.520 --> 57:24.557
Sagar, in turn, 
brought Shiva and Srikanth along. 


57:24.557 --> 57:27.027
Three of them are attending 
our meetings regularly. 


57:27.027 --> 57:29.695
Sagar even turned down a job offer 


57:29.695 --> 57:32.865
that conflicted with Bible principles. 


57:32.865 --> 57:35.935
One tract resulted in many Bible studies. 


57:35.935 --> 57:38.103
We can really see Jehovah’s blessing 


57:38.103 --> 57:41.000
on this form of public witnessing.


57:55.488 --> 57:58.290
Without a doubt, 
cart witnessing is being used 


57:58.290 --> 58:00.660
to help preach 
the good news of God’s Kingdom 


58:00.660 --> 58:05.000
“in all the inhabited earth 
for a witness to all the nations.”


58:19.678 --> 58:22.581
The examples we’ve seen in this program 


58:22.582 --> 58:25.319
truly highlight how Jehovah and Jesus 


58:25.318 --> 58:29.588
use all of us to get 
an unprecedented work accomplished.


58:29.588 --> 58:32.491
We’ve seen how young brothers are trained 


58:32.492 --> 58:34.894
to take the lead in the congregations, 


58:34.893 --> 58:37.130
how videos are produced 
around the world 


58:37.130 --> 58:39.032
for our spiritual benefit, 


58:39.032 --> 58:43.302
the work that goes into better 
utilizing our Kingdom Halls, 


58:43.302 --> 58:46.572
how wisdom from Jehovah 
benefits our construction work, 


58:46.572 --> 58:51.544
and how appropriate it is to praise 
our heavenly Father for all his works. 


58:51.543 --> 58:53.378
And last, 


58:53.378 --> 58:56.983
we were encouraged to continue 
in our public witnessing efforts 


58:56.983 --> 59:00.018
as we clearly see Jehovah’s blessing. 


59:00.018 --> 59:04.456
Yes, we are proud 
to be Jehovah’s Witnesses. 


59:04.457 --> 59:08.360
This is the best organization on earth.


59:08.360 --> 59:10.095
To conclude, 


59:10.095 --> 59:14.033
we’d like to share 
this postcard from Iceland. 


59:14.033 --> 59:17.103
Almost 335,000 people live 


59:17.103 --> 59:19.671
on this North Atlantic island nation, 


59:19.672 --> 59:23.000
of which about 380 are Jehovah’s Witnesses.


59:24.510 --> 59:27.480
Iceland is known 
for being the land of ice and fire, 


59:27.480 --> 59:30.717
as it has both a lot of volcanic activity 


59:30.717 --> 59:33.285
and Europe’s largest glacier. 


59:33.285 --> 59:35.120
In their free time, 


59:35.120 --> 59:38.490
the Witnesses in Iceland 
enjoy hiking in the beautiful nature


59:38.490 --> 59:42.928
or riding on horseback 
on Icelandic horses.


59:42.928 --> 59:46.765
The preaching work  
in Iceland began in 1929. 


59:46.765 --> 59:51.637
Brother Lindal was the only publisher 
on the island for nearly 18 years. 


59:51.637 --> 59:54.540
Today, the 380 publishers conduct 


59:54.540 --> 59:58.010
approximately 270 Bible studies, 


59:58.010 --> 59:59.912
and almost 700 people


59:59.912 --> 1:00:04.617
attended the Memorial of Christ’s death 
last year.


1:00:04.617 --> 1:00:07.820
In the winter, 
the sun is up for only a few hours. 


1:00:07.820 --> 1:00:11.090
While the Witnesses 
use the limited sunlight wisely


1:00:11.090 --> 1:00:13.893
—going from door to door 
or business witnessing—


1:00:13.893 --> 1:00:16.000
they are not scared by the darkness. 


1:00:18.030 --> 1:00:21.833
Some congregations use tiny lights 
on their public witnessing carts 


1:00:21.833 --> 1:00:25.338
so that the passersby will see the carts.


1:00:25.338 --> 1:00:28.606
Also, the weather in Iceland 
can change quickly. 


1:00:28.607 --> 1:00:33.145
To prevent literature from being damaged 
by rain or other weather elements, 


1:00:33.145 --> 1:00:37.917
some congregations use plastic covers 
on the literature.


1:00:37.917 --> 1:00:40.654
In 2011, a Polish group was established 


1:00:40.653 --> 1:00:42.788
in the capital city of Reykjavik, 


1:00:42.788 --> 1:00:47.000
and in 2016, a congregation 
with over 40 publishers was formed. 


1:00:48.928 --> 1:00:51.000
Today, they conduct over 20 Bible studies.


1:00:53.465 --> 1:00:56.768
All the brothers and sisters in Iceland 
send their warm Christian love. 


1:00:56.768 --> 1:01:00.138
We pray that Jehovah will continue 


1:01:00.138 --> 1:01:03.676
to bless their efforts in praising his name. 


1:01:03.677 --> 1:01:05.712
This is JW Broadcasting 


1:01:05.712 --> 1:01:16.707
from the world headquarters 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

